consistent with being\nuniformly distributed between 1.00 and 1.25 Jovian radii, but there are too few\nin the sample to map this distribution in detail.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Jan 2006 14:57:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
